What’s DogecoinEV? A community-driven fork of Dogecoin/Pepecoin, inspired by Elon Musk’s high-throughput blockchain vision. With 10 MB block sizes and optimized protocols, it offers faster transactions, lower fees, and scalability for real-world use.

Why funds were left: We trusted the exchange to secure our assets while prepping 4 possible listing—a misstep we own. This is a hiccup, not a halt. We’re pushing for alt exchange listings for now & prepping major updates to rebuild trust & momentum. Community is our backbone.
